item.title: How do i go into other people's servers
item.dc:creator: @gho5t gho5t
item.description:
@gho5t wrote:

Lmao your name is noobs are bad but youre asking the same question that every other noob asks…

Go to server advertisement board and find a servers ip, (it should be something like this: ScapeScape.no-ip.info)
On the moparscape client, and look in the top left hand corner where it says file. Click on that and click “new server” Then put in the IP. If the server has a specific port, put that in the box that comes up when you click “new port”… Jeez im sick of people asking this…
